The paper deals with image reconstruction from sub-Nyquist data and ghost correction in MRI, which are topics related to computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves optimization problems and regularization techniques, which are relevant to information theory (cs.IT) and mathematical modeling (cs.MM). Additionally, the paper uses numerical methods to solve the optimization problems, which falls under numerical analysis (cs.NA).
